{"author":"Michael Giver","data":{"alias":"dust-biome-kelp","assignee":"giverm","description":"GH #752. Fast-follow to #751. Update ExclusionDeterminationService to iterate enabled exclusions in Exclusion.priority_order, stop at first true (== best while priority is static), record/return that one. Out of scope: Data Source Registry. RISK (PM 2026-07-07): stop-at-first == best only while durability is a static list; revisit when durability goes dynamic.","id":"9b54-ed2c-2eb8-4035","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"ExclusionDeterminationService: return highest-priority exclusion instead of unsorted list"},"env_id":"7fda8af9-5f39-45e1-9caf-59ffda62ec19","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783434445422795001,"uuid":"6e264e08-be9f-4b8e-b6a2-38152acce100"}